Example ackermann implementation under external_src/ros_controllers/ackermann_steering_controller/test/common/

Network note, the ackerman_steering_controller seems to ignore the ROS_MASTER_URI setting and instead uses the URI/hostname
of the master itself that is set outside of hosts. Modify etc/hosts with the URI set to the hostname.